      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>42</offset>
        <text>Fisheries have rarely been 'sustainable'.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>84</offset>
        <text>Rather, fishing has induced serial depletions, long masked by improved technology, geographic expansion and exploitation of previously spurned species lower in the food web.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>258</offset>
        <text>With global catches declining since the late 1980s, continuation of present trends will lead to supply shortfall, for which aquaculture cannot be expected to compensate, and may well exacerbate.
</text>
